<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>lecture in something • lecture on something</xh5><p> <i>lecture in something—</i>give lectures in a subject to a group of students: Dr. Watson <u>lectures in</u> English literature.</p><p> <i>lecture on something—</i>1. lecture to students on a specific topic: This term he is <u>lecturing on</u> the nineteenth-century novelists. 2. give a long talk on a topic to a group of people: He goes round the country <u>lecturing on</u> the evils of drink.</p> </entry>
